name: cancer
description: This coin was born from a passionate mission: to unite us all in boldly declaring “F cancer!”* Together, we have the power to make a real difference—raising critical awareness and generating life-changing funds to support the fight against cancer. This cause is deeply personal to me, and I’m fully committed to ensuring its success. I will be donating live on stream to cancer awareness organizations, guaranteeing full transparency and delivering genuine impact to those who need it most. This isn’t just a project; it’s a movement of hope, strength, and defiance against a disease that affects so many. Let’s band together, achieve incredible goals, and create a lasting legacy. With unwavering commitment and diamond hands, we will hold strong—united forever in the fight to conquer cancer. Let’s make history together.
